(45,0,0,43348,28070, 'You''ve Been Around!', 'Well, look at ye!$B$BAnd I thought I had seen some things in this icy place! It seems obvious to this dwarf that you have the fire of the explorer burning in your eyes.$B$BWear this tabard with pride. That way your friends will know who to ask for directions when the time comes!$B$BKeep on the move!$B$BBrann Bronzebeard'), -- Explore Northrend
(46,78,78,0,0, '', ''), -- World Explorer
(230,72,0,0,0, '', ''), -- Battlemaster
(456,139,139,0,0, '', ''), -- Realm First! Obsidian Slayer
(614,0,0,44223,29611, 'For the Alliance!', 'War rages throughout our lands. Only the bravest heroes dare challenge strike the Horde where it hurts them most. You are among such heroes.$B$BThe blows you have delivered to the leadership of the Horde will open the door for our final assault. The Horde will bow down to the might of the Alliance.$B$BYour deeds will not go unrewarded. Ride on proudly!$B$B--Your King'), -- For The Alliance!
(619,0,0,44224,4949, 'For The Horde!', 'In this time of great turmoil true heroes rise from the misery. You are one such great hero.$B$BWar is upon us. Your efforts will further our cause on Azeroth. Your great feats shall go rewarded. Take this prize of Orgrimmar and ride to glory.$B$BFor the Horde!$B$BWarchief Thrall'), -- For The Horde!
