(876,0,0,43349,29533, 'I''ve been watching you, kid.', 'You''ve got quite a knack for throwing down in that arena. Keep this. Wear it with pride. Now get back in there and show them how it''s done!$B$BUncle Sal'), -- Brutally Dedicated
