(1250,0,0,40653,28951, 'Stinker''s New Home', 'I''ve heard how well you take care of our furry friends. I hope you don''t mind but I must get Stinker a new home. He just refuses to play nice with others.$B$BPlease make sure to feed him twice a day. And um... he has a thing for black cats.$B$B--Breanni'), -- Shop Smart, Shop Pet...Smart
